      <description>&lt;p&gt;Kovarex enrichment is the uranium processing upgrade that turns waste into fuel. Without it, &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/icon/uranium.png&#34; alt=&#34;uranium&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Uranium&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA; &amp;gt;}} uranium ore yields mostly U-238 鈥?barely enough U-235 to keep a single reactor running.&lt;div class=&#34;pro-tip&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TL;DR:&lt;/strong&gt; Kovarex centrifuges convert 40 U-238 + 40 U-235 → 41 U-238 + 1 U-235. Net: -40 U-238, +1 U-235 per cycle. Build 3 centrifuges per reactor. Kickstart requires 40 U-235 accumulated first.&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA; &amp;gt;}}&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/diagrams/kovarex-loop.svg&#34; alt=&#34;Kovarex enrichment loop — uranium ore processing, enrichment centrifuge, and fuel cell production&#34; class=&#34;schema-diagram&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; width=&#34;900&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA; &amp;gt;}}&lt;/p&gt;</description>
